### 2.2 架构改进方案

#### 改进 1: 实时数据推送机制 🔴 P0

**问题**: AutoIterationEngine 无法将实时数据推送到 Dashboard

**解决方案**:
```typescript
// src/auto-iteration.ts

import { getServices } from './dashboard/server';

export class AutoIterationEngine {
  private realtimeService?: RealtimeService;

  async start() {
    // 启动 Dashboard
    const dashboard = await import('./dashboard/server');
    await dashboard.startDashboard();

    // 获取实时服务
    const services = dashboard.getServices();
    this.realtimeService = services.realtimeService;

    // 执行迭代
    while (this.isRunning) {
      await this.runIteration();
    }
  }

  private async runIteration() {
    // 迭代开始
    await this.realtimeService?.broadcast({
      event: 'iteration.started',
      data: { iteration: this.iterationCount }
    });

    // Phase 1: 产品经理
    await this.realtimeService?.broadcast({
      event: 'phase.started',
      data: { phase: 'product_manager' }
    });

    const analysis = await this.productManager.executeAndCollect(...);

    await this.realtimeService?.broadcast({
      event: 'phase.completed',
      data: { phase: 'product_manager', result: analysis }
    });

    // ... 其他 Phase 类似处理
  }
}
```

**工作量**: 2 天 | **预期收益**: 实时监控延迟 < 500ms

